data.description: Location, Location, Location. Not much more is needed here. This home has been newly improved with new tile floors, painted cabinets, real wood interior wall panels with fresh designer colors. The kitchen is as cozy as your favorite child hood memory, with just the right amount of space for the chef to prepare meals. The kitchen is located just off the den/dining room. The floor plan is complete with Large Rooms and plenty of storage and space to spread out. There is a lot of home here and the updates are sweet and simply inviting. The Extra Large lot in the front and back yards is really something special. The land this home sits on is something to see. There is room in both spaces for your imagination to run wild. It's perfect for the buyer who wants space inside and outside. This home is charming with such character that speaks volumes about the neighborhood and history of the area.
